## Docker build
## docker build -t fastapi-todo .

## Docker run
## docker run -p 8000:8000 --add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway fastapi-todo

## Default port: 8000
## Postgres on host-gateway:5432


## BACKEND ## (Default: SQLITE3)
# If using postgres, set env var DB=POSTGRES or run using following command:
# docker run -p 8000:8000 --env-file=.env_postgres --add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway fastapi-todo
